snippet.title: WonderSwan - SD Gundam Eiyuuden: Kishi Densetsu trailer
snippet.description: There are two versions of this game, Kishi Densetsu and Musha Densetsu. This is a trailer for the Kishi version (works on both WonderSwan color and monochrome).
